  "title": "Launch of the 2025 Partnership for Good Grant",
  "description": "Advance Solutions and ServiceNow.org announce the grant program, dedicating up to $2M in technology, licensing, expert hours, and financial support to four nonprofits. The goal: modernize operations in disaster and community support, enabling nonprofits to focus on core missions.",
